<i>- During the day, they concealed</i>

15:34.433 --> 15:38.427
the enlarged grates
by creating false fronts

15:38.512 --> 15:40.939
<i>with a grate and cardboard</i>

15:41.098 --> 15:44.433
<i>painted to look like
the prison walls.</i>

15:44.526 --> 15:45.935
- They were able
to actually secure

15:46.028 --> 15:48.354
some of the actual paint
