15:51.858 --> 15:53.284
<i>so it perfectly matches.</i>

15:53.369 --> 15:54.610
<i>This was not something that was</i>

15:54.695 --> 15:56.037
just in place for two weeks.

15:56.121 --> 15:57.538
These were things
that were, you know,

15:57.623 --> 15:59.115
being utilized
for months and months.

15:59.208 --> 16:02.451
So they were actually
pretty compelling

16:02.536 --> 16:05.037
in terms of how
they crafted these.

16:05.122 --> 16:08.624
<i>- Covering their tracks
turns out to be the easy part.</i>

16:08.717 --> 16:10.960
<i>The hardened steel bolts
on the vent</i>

16:11.044 --> 16:13.638
<i>are almost impossible to cut.</i>

16:13.722 --> 16:16.391
<i>And the vent
is above the cellblock,</i>

16:16.475 --> 16:20.895
<i>exposed to any guard
