16:20.980 --> 16:24.557
<i>The escapees need a way
to work without being seen.</i>

16:24.641 --> 16:28.486
<i>♪ ♪</i>

16:28.570 --> 16:31.406
<i>- Allen West came up
with a really good plan</i>

16:31.565 --> 16:33.658
<i>to hide in plain view.</i>

16:33.817 --> 16:37.069
His job was to not just
paint the ceiling

16:37.154 --> 16:40.915
of the cell house,
but also to remove the debris

16:41.000 --> 16:42.825
that he encountered
along the way.

16:42.909 --> 16:45.253
And those areas
on top of the cell blocks

16:45.412 --> 16:47.005
<i>were not often traveled</i>

16:47.089 --> 16:48.497
<i>and they were dusty
as all get out,</i>

16:48.582 --> 16:50.249
<i>and lots of paint chips
