16:50.333 --> 16:52.418
<i>So he made a mess one day</i>

16:52.502 --> 16:56.255
<i>and swept all of that debris
down the tiers.</i>

16:56.339 --> 16:57.840
<i>Alcatraz had this reputation</i>

16:57.924 --> 17:00.184
<i>for having the shiniest
concrete floor</i>

17:00.269 --> 17:02.094
<i>in all of the land.</i>

17:02.187 --> 17:04.847
<i>It just wasn't fit
