17:26.712 --> 17:28.204
<i>that he would like to put up</i>

17:28.297 --> 17:31.457
blankets to completely enclose

17:31.541 --> 17:33.292
<i>above the cell block.</i>

17:33.376 --> 17:35.386
- His job wasn't that long.

17:35.545 --> 17:38.639
These drop cloths
were up there for months.

17:38.799 --> 17:41.392
<i>- The guards are fooled,</i>

17:41.477 --> 17:43.811
<i>but the rest
