They stood to benefit a lot

17:52.154 --> 17:54.072
if they would've
alerted an officer

17:54.156 --> 17:55.981
that there was
an escape going on.

17:56.066 --> 17:57.658
<i>And it really gives credit
to, you know,</i>

17:57.743 --> 17:59.744
<i>the entire inmate population</i>

17:59.903 --> 18:02.246
<i>who worked with them
collectively</i>

18:02.405 --> 18:04.832
<i>to ensure that
they were successful.</i>

18:04.917 --> 18:06.659
<i>- They try to
protect each other.</i>

18:06.743 --> 18:08.669
<i>Even if you hate the guy
