18:47.033 --> 18:48.543
<i>- I think it just goes to show</i>

18:48.627 --> 18:50.119
<i>they left no stone uncovered</i>

18:50.203 --> 18:52.380
and tried to cover
every single track

18:52.464 --> 18:54.799
so that if they did
go up and investigate,

18:54.958 --> 18:57.126
<i>there would be nothing
to tip them off.</i>

18:57.219 --> 18:58.636
<i>- That's gonna be their escape,</i>

18:58.795 --> 19:00.888
